message.body: Any interest in free night at Franklin institute tonight?
Yes, but I'm supposed to be meeting someone for drinks and I'm not sure where/when yet...
When are you thinking about going?
Ok! Drinks are at 7:30 in my neighborhood. I can probably be at the Franklin by 6, which would give us an hour at least. Would that work for you?
Idk if I'll be there by 6. I'm coming from blue Bell
What's your best guess on time?
Only 76 during rush hour knows... Wishful thinking 6:30
Crap. Well, I'll probably head down no matter what (you piqued my interest) so let me know when you get there and maybe we can at least meet up for a few minutes
Hey, my boss got back from London right before I was leaving work and needed a bunch of stuff, so I was late getting home. I'm headed down to the Parkway now
I'm still at work... Don't think I'll make it
Ok, see you another time then
